Detailed Description

cvmx_ipd_port_qos_::_cnt

IPD_PORT_QOS_X_CNT = IPD PortX QOS-0 Count A counter per port/qos. Counter are originzed in sequence where the first 8 counter (0-7) belong to Port-0 QOS 0-7 respectively followed by port 1 at (8-15), etc Ports 0-3, 32-43
